      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented QA procedures and version control meets MRL 2 requirement of Gradation 1.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v19.2 is a commercially validated solver with documented software quality assurance processes including regression testing and release validation. Version control and change management procedures are maintained by the vendor. Gradation 1 requirements are satisfied."
    },
    {
