      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes standard benchmark verification cases relevant to internal rotating flow. Gradation 1 sufficient at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against standard CFD benchmark problems including lid-driven cavity and rotating channel flow. Published verification reports from the vendor confirm second-order spatial accuracy. Gradation 1 is met."
