      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares impeller topology and flow regime (Re ~ 10^4) with the CPB device under assessment. Operating conditions span the clinical flow range. Validation activities are directly relevant to the COU. Gradation 2 achieved."
