      "rationale": "Blood rheological properties were taken from ASTM F1841 and published literature (viscosity 0.0035 Pa·s, density 1056 kg/m³, hematocrit 40%). Sensitivity to input variation was not formally quantified, consistent with MRL 2 Gradation 1."
